  <div class="v8-contain">
    <span class="v8-annot">Live examples — AI-designed, on plekify.com</span>
    <h2 class="v8-sh">What the pipeline produces<br><em>in practice.</em></h2>
    <p class="v8-body v8-prose" style="margin-top:.35rem">Each itinerary has two views: a client-facing presentation and a separate operator view containing all operational detail — property contacts, logistics notes, source provenance, and commercial structure — not visible to guests. The dual-view distinction matters because operators already manage separate client and trade-partner versions of the same itinerary.</p>
